    {
      "id": "07f702d8-2701-4274-88a8-0da5128d8654",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "After optimization, the authors employ multiple ML algorithms to predict student performance and see impact of dataset. Tecnhiques used involve NB, LRNN, ANN and kNN. results show that combining HHO and LRNN outperformed all other classifiers in benchmarked dataset with 92% accuracy.",
